== Tameddurt ==


'''Mulud At Mamar''' i lmed, imi yella d amecttuh, deg aɣerbaz n taddart-is. Deg 1928 yemsafr-ed ɣer Lmrruk ɣef taxxamt n unat-is g Ribat. Rebɛa isegassen mbeɛd yuɣal-ed ɣer Lezzayer ad ikemmel almad-ines deg uɣerbaz iwumi qqaren “Bugeaud” di temdint n Lezzayer; kra n isegassen mbeɛd, imi ikeml-ed almad-is, yeğğa-d aneggaru agi ɣef yewin aɣerbaz nniden iwumi qqaren ''“Louis-le-Grand”'' di temdint n Paris iwakken ad yuɣal d aselmad.


Deg 1939 ikcem-ed ɣef tazemmalt, asmi Ttrad n Ddunit II tebda-d, lameɛna yeţwasereh-ed deg Tuber 1940: Lmulud Mɛemri ikcem-ed ɣef aɣiwen n tisekwla n uɣerbaz n temdint Ledzayer. 


Deg 1942, mbeɛd aggwad n Lmarican ɣef Tafriqt ugafa, Mɛemri yeţnuda ɣef tazemmalt s tikkelt tis snat; yezra igran n imenɣi n '''Talyan''', '''Fransa''', akk-d n '''Lalman'''


Di taggara n ttrad, 1945, yeswejd-ed, deg Paris, ɣef tamenyugart n iselmaden; mbeɛd ayagi yuɣal-ed ɣef Lezzayer deg Ctember 1947.  Yesselmad deg Lemdiya akk-d Ben-ɛaknun yerna yura-d taktabt-is tamezwarut, '''Tadart i yeţţwaţun''' (''La Colline oubliée'') deg 1952. lemeɛna seddaw n tiggermemt n temɛict deg Lezzayer yeğğa-d temdint n Ledzayer deg 1957.


Seg 1957 armi 1962, Mulud At Mamar iɛacc g Lmerruk.


Deg 1962, armi terbeh azarug-ines, Mulud At Mamar ikccm-ed ɣef Lezzayer. Seg 1965 armi 1972, yesselmad Tamaziɣt deg tasdawit n temdint n Ledzayer seddaw n uferkaw n amezruy n igduden; ayagi mbeɛd tagdelt n islemaden n tamaziɣt deg 1962 ɣef ddemma n unabad n Lezzayer. 

'''Mulud At Mamar''' yeslmad tamziɣt seddaw tamagazt i hersen n tamsulta n sser n unabad n Lezzayer.


Deg 1969 Mɛemri isdukkel idrisen n umedyaz Azwaw Si Mohend.


1969 armi 1980 yella d anemhal n iferkawen n idlesen n yemdanen,  amezruy atrar, akk-d  amezruy n igduden.


Deg 1980, mbeɛd tagdelt n usarag-is deg Tizi Wezzu ɣef tamedyazt taqdimt n wegdud Azwaw, bdan ccwal n '''Tafsut Tamaziɣt'''.


1982, ixelq-ed deg Paris '''Tuddsa n Islemaden & Tagmi n Tamaziɣt''' (''Centre d Etudes de Recherches Amazighes'' ''CERAM''), akk-d tasɣunt ''Awal''. Deg 1988 Mulud Mɛemri yetwaqbel am ttbib s tamanegt deg tasdawit n ''la Sorbonne''.


'''Mulud At Mamar''' yemut deg ass 26 n Furar 1989, lameɛna ahric ameqran n medden sɛan ccek belli anabad Aɛrab n Lezzayer i t-yenɣan deg tmeddit nni; ayagi merra d ayen i gzemren a d-ssefhem s tideţ 
, akken ilaq, amexix agi.

'''Mulud At Mamar''' yeğğa later akk-d tikta meqren atker n ahric ameqran n imalwayen ayen llan deg umezruy n wegdud Azwaw; akter n Masnsen, akter n Yugurtan, akter n Lkahina, Mɛemri yebda-d abrid i yeţţawin ɣef umneɛ n rruh n wegdud Azwaw, agdud-nneɣ.

== Tajmilt i Dda Lmulud : Amussnaw nni... ==

'''Sɣur Sadi Qasi, aɣmis izuran, uṭṭun 17, Meɣres 2007'''



Ilul Mouloud Mammeri di 28 décembre 1917 di Tewrirt Mimun (At Yanni). Asmi yesɛa 12 n yiseggasen, iruḥ ɣer ɛemmis di Lmerruk. Din dɣa i yebda leqraya-ines anda yeqqim 04 n yiseggasen, yuɣal yekcem ɣer Lezzayer tamaneɣt di 1934 akken ad ikemmel taɣuri-ines di Tesnawit Bugeand. 

 
Yebda leqraya taɛlayant di Lpari di tesnawit Louis Le Grand, akken ad iheggi i temzizelt n unekcum ɣer l’ENS. Cwi ṭraḍ wis sin n umaḍal yesxerb-as aẓeṭṭa. 

 
Wwin-t ɣer lɛesker di 1939, serḥen-as-id di Ṭuber 1940. Ijerred ɣer tesdawit n tsekla di Lezzayer. Uɣalen ɛiwden iwin-t ɣer lɛesker asmi d-tekcem Marikan deg yimenɣan n Ṭelyan, n Fransa akked Lalman. 

 
Akken kan ifak ṭraḍ, Mammeri ihegga di Lpari timzizzelt n Professorat n tsekla, dɣa yuɣal-d ɣer Lzzayer di 1947. Yesɣer di Lemdiyya, yuɣal ɣer Ben Aknun. Sin ɣer-s, yeffeɣ si tmurt di 1957, imi tezmek fell-as. 

 
Yeqqim di Lmerruk si 1957 almi d 1962. Mi d-yuɣal ɣer tmurt, yeṭṭef Almmas n unadi di tussna n talsa d umezruy aqdim (CRAPE) i d-yezgan di Lezzayer tamaneɣt almi d 1979, yerna daɣ yesɣar di tasdawit n Lezzayer. 

 
Yesɣer Tamaziɣt di tesdawit n Lezzayer si 1962 ɣer 1969 asmi akken i tegguma tneɣlaft teɛna temsalt ad sseɣren tussna n talsa (Anthropologie) akked Ethnologie imi, ɛlaḥsab-ines, “tigi d tussniwin n umnekcam, ur ilaq ara ad tent-sseɣren di tesdawit n tmurt n Lezzayer!“ Yuɣal yessɣer Tamaziɣt, kan akka s lebɣi-is almi d 1973. 

 
Di Meɣres 1980, ɛerḍen-t-id yinelmaden n tesdawit n Tizi Wezzu akken ad d yawi asarag ɣef “yisefra n Zik n teqbaylit”, imḍebbren n tmurt gguman ad t-ǧǧen. D anect-a i d seba n tedyanin n Tefsut imaziɣen n 80.

 
Deg useggas 1982, yesnulfa-d di Lpari Alammas n tezrawiyin d unadi di Tmaziɣt ( CERAM ). Ma di 1985, d tasɣunt “Awal” i d-yessufeɣ. Yerna daɣ, ixeddem isaragen ɣef tutlayt d yidles d tsekla n tamaziɣt di (IHESS), yiwen n uɣerbaz i yelhan d unadi di tussniwin n tmetti. 

 
Ma d ayen yura Mouloud Mammeri, netta d yiwen seg yimura yessersen lsas i tsekla n Tmurt n yimaziɣen s tutlayt tafransist. Ungalen-is ttwassnen di ddunit meṛṛa. Dɣa sin seg-sen “L’opium et le bâton” akked “La colline oubliée” (neɣ Tawrirt yettwxattun) rran-ten d isura, yiwen s teɛrabt n Lezzayer, yessufeɣ-it-id Ahmed Rachedi, ma d wis sin s tamaziɣt, yessufeɣ-it-id Abderrahmane Bouguermouh. 

 
Akken yella d amaru i yella daɣ d amusnaw n tutlayt d yidles n tmaziɣt. Yewwet ɣef tamaziɣt s yidles d tussna. Ɣas yeɣra tutlayin nniḍen, yeṭṭef di teqbaylit i t-id-yessekren. Dɣa ur yeǧǧi yiwet : Yura ɣef tmetti, ɣef umezruy, ɣef tsekla, ɣef tutlayt… 

 
Igmer-d awalen, isefra n At Zik, yeṭṭef-iten di lkaɣeḍ, ixdem ilugan n tira i tutlayt tečča timawit. Ayen akk yura, seg yisefra n At Zik d wid n Si Muḥ Umḥend yerra-ten ɣer tefransist akken ad ten-fehmen ula d ibarraniyen. Yessufeɣ ayen yeffren di Tudrin akin i lebḥer. 

 
Ur yeǧǧi Lmerruk, ur yeǧǧi Itergiyen, ur yeǧǧi Gurara, ur yeǧǧi Icawiyen… asmi akken yekker i tutlayt n tamaziɣt d yidles n yal timetti n yimaziɣen. Amawal, ahellil du Gourara, Amawal tafransist-tatergit d amedya, imi tiṭ-is ad-d-yejmeɛ/yelqeḍ ayen yellan yakan, ad yesnerni daɣ tutlayt s usulfu n wawalen  imaynuten ara yeddun d lweqt/wakud i deg yettidir. 

 
I waken kan ad nesmekti, asmi akken tettwakes tamaziɣt si tesdawit n Lezzayer, d Mouloud Mammeri i yessutren Ahmed Taleb, aneɣlaf n tterbegga n yimiren, n lḥukuma n H.Boumediène, di octobre1965. 

 
Deg yiseggasen nni dɣa, i yebdan yilmeẓyen n tmurt n Leqbayel ara ttissinen/ttagmen sit ala n tmussni, werǧin yezɛif neɣ yergim yiwen. Rur-s, tilufa ferrunt s ttwab d lmeɛqul. S tussna d tmussni. 

 
D netta dɣa i d-yemmeslayen ɣef tutlayin tiɣerfanin di Lezzayer, iwumi kksen azal yemḍebbren d yibeɛtiyen; yenna deg yiwen n usarag yexdem di 09 meɣres 1984 di tesdawit n Montréal, Kanada; “Tutlayin i ttmeslayen s tidett yizzayriyen d taɛrabt tazzayrit d tamaziɣt. Maca ur sɛint ara amkan   am taɛrabt tufsiḥt. D taɛrabt tufsiḥt kan i yes-s stɛerfen, d tutlayt tunsibt ɣas ulamma ur tt- yesmeslay yiwen. Taɛrabt tazzayrit d tmaziɣt d tutlayin n yizzayriyen akken ma allan, maca ur sɛint amkan unṣib. Llant s tidet di tilawt, meɛni ulac-itent di tmendawt” 

 
Ma d taluft-nni i yes-s bɣan ad ssamsen amusnaw, aṭas ahat ur tt-neẓri. Yuzzel wawal di 80 ɣef akken  Mouloud Mammeri ur yeddi ara deg webrid n tegrawla n Lezzayer.

 
I wid ur neẓri, asmi akken tiweḍ temsalt n Lezzayer ɣer Ugraw n tmura yeduklen (ONU), d Mammeri i yuran aḍris n yimceggɛen n tmurt n Lezzayer, M’hemmed Yazid. Aḍris-agi yestenya-t Mammeri s yisem n Keddour. (I wid yebɣan an ɣren aḍris- agi, ad ɣren tisɣunin “Awal” akked “Iẓuran” uṭṭun 2 (furar 1999).

 
D tidet, Mammeri yettekki di tegrawla, asmi yekkat ɣef tamaziɣt, wwten akk amek ara t- ssamsen, netta ur yuklal. 

 
I wakken kan ad d-nesmekti, M. Mammeri yemmut ass n 25 février 1989 deg ubrid n Ɛin Defla, asmi d-yuɣal si temlilit di Ujda (Lmerruk) i deg yexdem asarag ɣef timawit. 

 
Aṭas n yixxamen n yidles i semman fell-as. Tasdawit n Tizi wezzu tuɣal s yissem-is. Aṭas n yicennayen i as-yerran/yettaran tajmilt. Yal aseggas, xeddmen yiselmaden isaragen ama di tesdawin ama anda nniḍen. Ulac win izemren ad yenker ayen yexdem ɣef/ i tamaziɣt. D netta dɣa i as-yennan : “win ibɣan tamaziɣt, yissin tira-s” 

 
Ihi, win ibɣan ad yerr tajmilt i “Dda Lmulud” iɣer ayen yura d wayen uran fell-as !

